- Store prompts and magic strings like model names in constant files for easy management
- Implement proper error handling and fallback mechanisms for AI API calls
- Use environment variables to store sensitive API keys and credentials
- Implement rate limiting and caching strategies to optimize API usage
- Document your prompts and expected outputs for better maintainability
- Use type-safe interfaces for AI responses to ensure data integrity
